abstract: NFL Roundup. Winless Miami Dolphins will start Matt Moore at quarterback in place of Chad Henne, who will have shoulder surgery following injury. Sign quarterback Sage Rosenfels as backup.
snippet: Winless Miami will start Matt Moore at quarterback in place of Chad Henne, who will have shoulder surgery after being injured last Sunday.
lead_paragraph: Winless Miami will start Matt Moore at quarterback in place of Chad Henne, who will have shoulder surgery after being injured last Sunday.

headline.main: With Henne Done for Season, Dolphins Sign Rosenfels and Will Start Moore
headline.print_headline: With Henne Done for Season, Dolphins Sign Rosenfels and Will Start Moore
headline.seo: Dolphins’ Henne to Miss Rest of Season
